CSS3 Width Hint for Responsive Webdesigns by Ingo Krumbein

This small CSS File adds a line to the bottom of your Page with the Information of the Width.
It is perfect to see whats happens on which Resolution with your Responsive Design.

Version 1.0.0

Available Widths:
- Less than 360px
- 360px up to 480px
- 480px up to 640px
- 640px up to 800px
- 800px up to 960px
- 960px up to 1120px
- 1120px up to 1280px
- 1280px up to 1440px
- 1440px up to 1680px
- 1680px and higher